---
import SectionLabel from "./SectionLabel.astro";
---

<section id="experience" class="section exp-section">
  <div class="container">

    <div class="exp-head">
      <SectionLabel label="Experiencia" />
      <span class="exp-count">3 roles · 2023–presente</span>
    </div>

    <div class="exp-list">

      <!-- ── 1. Funeraria San Gabriel ── -->
      <div class="exp-row">
        <div class="exp-row-header">
          <div class="exp-row-left">
            <h3 class="exp-company">Funeraria San Gabriel</h3>
            <span class="exp-role">Software Engineer</span>
          </div>
          <span class="exp-date">Jul 2024 – Presente</span>
        </div>
        <div class="exp-details">
          <ul class="exp-bullets">
            <li>Diseñé e implementé CRM funerario completo — desde el modelado de BD con Prisma ORM hasta el deployment en Railway con Docker</li>
            <li>Integré pasarela de pagos con webhooks en producción; manejo de estados en tiempo real</li>
            <li>Automaticé comunicaciones masivas a clientes vía integración con APIs de mensajería</li>
          </ul>
          <div class="exp-tags">
            <span class="tag">Node.js</span>
            <span class="tag">Prisma ORM</span>
            <span class="tag">PostgreSQL</span>
            <span class="tag">Docker</span>
            <span class="tag">Railway</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- ── 2. ShareFlow ── -->
      <div class="exp-row">
        <div class="exp-row-header">
          <div class="exp-row-left">
            <h3 class="exp-company">
              ShareFlow
              <span class="badge-wip">En construcción</span>
            </h3>
            <span class="exp-role">Co-Founder · Product Engineer</span>
          </div>
          <span class="exp-date">Oct 2024 – Presente</span>
        </div>
        <div class="exp-details">
          <ul class="exp-bullets">
            <li>Co-fundé startup DOOH y diseñé la arquitectura completa del ecommerce de publicidad en pantallas digitales</li>
            <li>Versión parcial en producción; cerrando flujo de pago e integrando proveedor de tótems en Envigado</li>
          </ul>
          <div class="exp-tags">
            <span class="tag">Next.js</span>
            <span class="tag">TypeScript</span>
            <span class="tag">Supabase</span>
            <span class="tag">Docker</span>
            <span class="tag">Railway</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- ── 3. Kodland ── -->
      <div class="exp-row">
        <div class="exp-row-header">
          <div class="exp-row-left">
            <h3 class="exp-company">Kodland</h3>
            <span class="exp-role">Python &amp; Web Instructor</span>
          </div>
          <span class="exp-date">Dic 2023 – Ago 2024</span>
        </div>
        <div class="exp-details">
          <ul class="exp-bullets">
            <li>Enseñé Python y desarrollo web a estudiantes de 8–16 años — desarrollé capacidad de traducir sistemas complejos a lenguaje claro</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .exp-section {
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .exp-section::before {
    content: "EXPERIENCE";
    position: absolute;
    top: 3rem;
    right: -1rem;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(5rem, 14vw, 11rem);
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    opacity: 0.032;
    pointer-events: none;
    user-select: none;
    white-space: nowrap;
    line-height: 1;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
  }

  .exp-head {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .exp-count {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }

  .exp-list {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  /* ── Row ── */
  .exp-row {
    border-bottom: var(--border);
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(20px);
    transition:
      opacity 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.22, 1, 0.36, 1),
      transform 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.22, 1, 0.36, 1);
  }

  .exp-row.visible { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  .exp-row:nth-child(1) { transition-delay: 0.05s; }
  .exp-row:nth-child(2) { transition-delay: 0.15s; }
  .exp-row:nth-child(3) { transition-delay: 0.25s; }

  .exp-row-header {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    padding-block: 1.875rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .exp-row-left {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.3rem;
  }

  .exp-company {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(1.375rem, 2.8vw, 1.875rem);
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    line-height: 1.1;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.6rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .exp-role {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.07em;
    color: var(--accent);
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .exp-date {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    white-space: nowrap;
    padding-top: 0.4rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  }

  .badge-wip {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 9px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.07em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--accent-text);
    background: var(--accent-light);
    border: 0.5px solid var(--accent);
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    padding: 2px 7px;
    vertical-align: middle;
  }

  /* ── Details ── */
  .exp-details {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.875rem;
    padding-bottom: 1.875rem;
  }

  .exp-bullets {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }

  .exp-bullets li {
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    font-weight: 300;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.6;
    padding-left: 1.1rem;
    position: relative;
    max-width: 72ch;
  }

  .exp-bullets li::before {
    content: "·";
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--accent);
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .exp-tags {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.35rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .exp-row-header { flex-direction: column; gap: 0.4rem; }
    .exp-date { padding-top: 0; }
  }
</style>

<script>
  const observer = new IntersectionObserver(
    (entries) => {
      entries.forEach((entry) => {
        if (entry.isIntersecting) entry.target.classList.add("visible");
      });
    },
    { threshold: 0.08 }
  );
  document.querySelectorAll(".exp-row").forEach((el) => observer.observe(el));
</script>
